data.text:
Yash Rocking star's real name is Naveen Kumar Gowda. He is a renowned actor from the Kannada Film Industry. Yash first appeared in the film Moggina Manasu, released in 2008, he played the male lead opposite his future wife Radhika.

KFG Chapter 1

Yash was last seen in the film KFG Chapter 1 released in 2018. The film was directed by Prashanth Neel and produced by Vijay Kiragandur under the banner Hombale films.

advertisement

The film cast actors including --Srinidhi Shetty, Vasishta N. Simha, Achyuth Kumar, Malavika Avinash. The film went on to gross Rs 250 crore at the box office.

Yash's upcoming movies:

KGF Chapter 2

Yash Rocking star's KGF Chapter 2 is an upcoming Indian Kannada-language film written and directed by Prashanth Neel and produced by Vijay Kiragandur under the banner Hombale Films.

The film will star Yash with Sanjay Dutt, Srinidhi Shetty, Raveena Tandon, and Prakash Raj.

KGF Chapter 2 is the most expensive Kannada film till now, with a budget of Rs 100 crore. The film was supposed to release in 2020 but due to the Covid-19 pandemic, the release has been postponed to 2021.

My Name Is Kirataka

Yash will also be seen in a romantic action film directed by Anil Kumar. Yash's upcoming film will be produced by Jayanna Bhogendra under the Jayanna Combines banner. The film will also feature Yash and Nandita Swetha.
